query:
SELECT 
  COUNT(*) as total_lenders,
  COUNT(CASE WHEN url IS NOT NULL AND url != '' THEN 1 END) as with_url,
  COUNT(CASE WHEN phone IS NOT NULL AND phone != '' THEN 1 END) as with_phone
FROM lenders;
